根據[[NPD_Group|NPD Group]]，Wii U在美國上市首周任天堂就將第一批庫存的400,000台主機全部售出，<ref name=NintenHardware>{{cite web|last=Reisigner|first=Don|title=Nintendo:1.2 million hardware units sold, 400,000 Wii U|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-57554183-235/nintendo-1.2-million-hardware-units-sold-400000-wii-u/|publisher=cnet.com|accessdate=2012-11-26|archive-date=2012-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121201134203/http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-57554183-235/nintendo-1.2-million-hardware-units-sold-400000-wii-u/}}</ref>整個11月總計售出425,000台主機。<ref name=NPD>{{cite web|title='Call of Duty,' Wii U can't stop video game slide|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2012/12/06/npd-video-game-sales-november/1752081/|publisher=[[Gannett_Company|Gannett Company]]|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|accessdate=2012-12-07|archive-date=2022-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325223120/https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2012/12/06/npd-video-game-sales-november/1752081/}}</ref>而英國上市的第一個週末總計銷售量為40,000台。<ref name=UK>{{cite web|last=Cook|first=Dane|url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/12/03/wii-u-40000-consoles-sold-over-uk-launch-weekend-report/comment-page-1/|publisher=VG247|accessdate=2012-12-03|title=Wii U: 40,000 Consoles Sold Over UK Launch Weekend – Report|archive-date=2012-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121208013754/http://www.vg247.com/2012/12/03/wii-u-40000-consoles-sold-over-uk-launch-weekend-report/comment-page-1/}}</ref>在日本，2012年12月間總計售出超過600,000台Wii U。<ref name=Japan>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/07/us-nintendo-console-sales-idUSBRE90605420130107|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2013-01-07|title=Year-end Wii U sales steady, says Nintendo chief|archive-date=2013-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130110055538/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/07/us-nintendo-console-sales-idUSBRE90605420130107}}</ref>根據NPD Group,，Wii U主機在美國上市後的41天間總計售出890,000台。<ref name=NintenHardware2>{{cite web|last=Reisigner|first=Don|title=Wii U sales surpass Wii's through first six weeks|url=http://www.news10.net/entertainment/gameguys/article/224725/99/Wii-U-sales-surpass-Wiis-through-first-six-weeks/|publisher=news10.net|accessdate=2013-01-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004232118/http://www.news10.net/entertainment/gameguys/article/224725/99/Wii-U-sales-surpass-Wiis-through-first-six-weeks/|archivedate=2013-10-04}}</ref>在2013年4月至6月間的銷售量為160,000台，比起前三個月（2013年1月至3月）的銷售量下滑了51%。<ref name="bbcsales">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-23515086 |title=Nintendo's Wii U sales disappoint |publisher=BBC |date=2013-07-31 |access-date=2013-10-03 |archive-date=2022-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325222940/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-23515086 }}</ref>

<!-- Q1/Q2 2013 -->
2013年1月Wii U在美國的銷售量為57,000台。<ref>{{cite web|last=Sinclair|first=Brendan|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-02-15-wii-u-sells-57-000-systems-in-january|title=Wii U sells 57,000 systems in January|date=2013-02-15|accessdate=2013-02-17|archive-date=2013-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217211347/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-02-15-wii-u-sells-57-000-systems-in-january}}</ref>相較之下，上一代的[[Wii|Wii]]在2007年1月售出了435,000台，同樣也是上市後兩個月的時間點。<ref name=January2013NPDSalesCNET>{{cite web |title=Uh-oh: Nintendo sold 57,000 Wii U units in the U.S. in January |author=Don Reisinger |url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-57569583-235/uh-oh-nintendo-sold-57000-wii-u-units-in-the-u.s-in-january/ |publisher=CNET |date=2013-02-15 |accessdate=2013-04-18 |archive-date=2013-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217000306/http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-57569583-235/uh-oh-nintendo-sold-57000-wii-u-units-in-the-u.s-in-january/ }}</ref>由於Wii U在美國和其他地區的銷售量低於預期，因此任天堂將2013[[財政年度|財政年度]]的銷售預測降低了17%，從550萬美元調降至400萬美元；<ref>{{cite web |author=Jason Evangelho |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/jasonevangelho/2013/01/30/nintendo-cuts-sales-projections-by-17-based-on-sluggish-wii-u-sales/ |title=Nintendo Cuts FY 2013 Sales Projections By 17% Based On Sluggish Wii U Sales |publisher=Forbes |date=2013-01-30 |accessdate=2013-02-06 |archive-date=2022-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325222940/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jasonevangelho/2013/01/30/nintendo-cuts-sales-projections-by-17-based-on-sluggish-wii-u-sales/ }}</ref>Wii U最後在該財政年度總共賣出350萬台。<ref name="2012sales">{{cite web |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/Innovation/2013/0130/Nintendo-admits-the-Wii-U-is-struggling-to-gain-traction |title=Nintendo Admits the Wii U Is Struggling to Gain Traction |last=Shaer |first=Matthew |publisher=Christian Science Publishing Society |work=The Christian Science Monitor |date=2013-01-30 |access-date=2013-10-03 |archive-date=2013-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131095101/http://www.csmonitor.com/Innovation/2013/0130/Nintendo-admits-the-Wii-U-is-struggling-to-gain-traction }}</ref>在2013年7月末，[[沃爾瑪|沃爾瑪]]在英國的子公司[[ASDA|ASDA]]，同時也是該國第二大的連鎖量販店，宣布他們並沒有銷售Wii U主機的計劃，但依然會銷售Wii U的部分遊戲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/421340/asda-suspends-wii-u-stock/|title=Asda suspends Wii U stock|last=Crossley|first=Rob|publisher=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|ComputerAndVideoGames.com]]|date=2013-07-29|accessdate=2013-07-30|archive-date=2013-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801065656/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/421340/asda-suspends-wii-u-stock/}}</ref>而許多遊戲零售商則持續強調他們對Wii U主機的支持，英國連鎖遊戲商店Game表示「我們完全支持所有的任天堂產品，包括Wii U」。<ref>{{cite news|last=Whitehead|first=Thomas|title=Specialist Retailers Emphasize Their Support for the Wii U|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/08/specialist_retailers_emphasize_their_support_for_the_wii_u|accessdate=2013-08-03|newspaper=Nintendo Life|date=2013-08-02|archive-date=2013-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130803191506/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/08/specialist_retailers_emphasize_their_support_for_the_wii_u}}</ref>

===停產===
2016年11月时，任天堂日本更新了Wii U的页面，并表示Wii U的日版将会在近期停产。<ref>Lumb, David. [https://www.engadget.com/2016/11/10/nintendo-confirms-it-will-end-wii-u-production-in-japan/ Nintendo confirms it will end Wii U production in Japan] {{Wayback|url=https://www.engadget.com/2016/11/10/nintendo-confirms-it-will-end-wii-u-production-in-japan/ |date=20200305094450 }}.Engadget.2016-11-11.[2016-11-11].</ref>2017年1月31日，任天堂宣布正式在全球停產Wii U，而Wii U也成為了任天堂歷史上生命週期最短的家用遊戲主機。<ref name="end">[http://www.gamespot.com/articles/wii-u-production-ends-worldwide/1100-6447419/ Wii U Production Ends Worldwide] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/wii-u-production-ends-worldwide/1100-6447419/ |date=20220415143121 }}.GameSpot.2017-01-31.[2017-02-01].</ref>

